<h1 id="firstHeading" class="firstHeading">
<span dir="auto">Premier Tournaments</span>
</h1>

<div id="bodyContent" class="mw-body-content">
<div id="siteSub">
</div>
<div id="contentSub">
</div>

<div id="mw-content-text" lang="en" dir="ltr" class="mw-content-ltr"><div class="mw-parser-output"><table width="100%" cellpadding="2" cellspacing="8" style="background:#6B6B8F; border-style:solid; border-width:2px; border-color:#9D9DB5">
<tbody><tr>
<td width="55%" valign="top" style="padding: 0; margin:0;">
<div style="width:100%">
</div>
<div style="clear: both; border: solid #9D9DB5; border-width: 1px 1px 0; background: #B7B8CD; color: black; padding: .1em;padding-top: .1em;padding-left: .1em;padding-right: .1em;padding-bottom: .1em;text-align: center;font-family: arial;font-size:100%;margin-bottom: 0px;"><div class="plainlinks" style="float:right;margin-bottom:.1em;font-size:80%; color: black"><a class="internal text" href="https://liquipedia.net/starcraft2/index.php?title=Premier_Tournaments&amp;action=edit"><span style="color: black">edit</span></a>&#160;&#160;
</div><h2 style="font-size:100%; font-weight:bold; border: none; margin: 0; padding:0; padding-bottom:.1em; color:black;"><span class="mw-headline" id="Tournaments">Tournaments</span></h2>
</div>
<div style="border: 1px solid #9D9DB5; border-top-width: 1px; vertical-align: top;background: #CFCEDE;opacity: 1; color: black; text-align: left; margin: 0 0 10px; padding: 1em;padding-top: .3em;">
<div style="float:right; width:32%">
</div>
<div class="tabs-static"><ul class="nav nav-tabs navigation-not-searchable tabs tabs10"><li><a href="/starcraft2/Portal:Leagues" title="Portal:Leagues">Introduction</a></li><li><a href="/starcraft2/Recent_Tournament_Results" title="Recent Tournament Results">Recent&#160;Results</a></li><li class="active"><a class="mw-selflink selflink">Premier&#160;Events</a></li><li><a href="/starcraft2/Major_Tournaments" title="Major Tournaments">Major&#160;Events</a></li><li><a href="/starcraft2/Minor_Tournaments" title="Minor Tournaments">Minor&#160;Events</a></li><li><a href="/starcraft2/Team_Tournaments" title="Team Tournaments">Team&#160;Events</a></li><li><a href="/starcraft2/Monthly_Tournaments" title="Monthly Tournaments">Monthly</a></li><li><a href="/starcraft2/Weekly_Tournaments" title="Weekly Tournaments">Weekly</a></li><li><a href="/starcraft2/Show_Matches" title="Show Matches">Show&#160;Matches</a></li><li><a href="/starcraft2/Female_Tournaments" title="Female Tournaments">Female&#160;Only</a></li></ul></div>
<p><br />
</p>
<center><b>Premier Tournaments offer an outstanding prize pool, are frequently played out offline, and feature the best players from all over the world. They are commonly held by well-established franchises and are considered especially prestigious amongst the community.</b></center>
<h2><span class="mw-headline" id="Legacy_of_the_Void_Tournaments">Legacy of the Void Tournaments</span></h2>
<h3><span class="mw-headline" id="2020">2020</span></h3>
<table class="sortable wikitable smwtable jquery-tablesorter" style="margin-left:0px; margin-right:auto;">
<tbody><tr>
<th width="60">Start
</th>
<th width="65">End
</th>
<th width="380">Name
</th>
<th width="90">Series
</th>
<th width="60">Prize&#160;pool
</th>
<th width="40">P#
</th>
<th width="135">Location
</th>
<th width="150">Winner
</th>
